===Keep going, it's a race against the clock{{subst:void|<!--202031502-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=companion|location=Artisanship Commission|update|I have just killed an abomination, but Ms. Jingliu has already disappeared. That was quick! I didn't see it coming. As the general's retainer, how could I lose to her? I need to hurry.}}
