{{Dialogue End}}

===Read the words left behind by Jingliu{{subst:void|<!--202031507-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=companion|location=Artisanship Commission|update|This is the end of the competition, Jingliu won. She challenges me to a bout of sword fight. Every time I try to go on the offense, she would be a step ahead of me. This lady doesn't seem to be satisfied with her achievement this whole way and wanted me to take an attack from her. I&mdash;I thought I would be the one to become the Sword Champion, but I didn't expect myself to be utterly decimated in this way.<br />In the last moment, I took her attack, her Killing Intent shook me to my core. Thank the heavens, it must be because I have never slacked in my training that I managed to survive. With someone like this on the Xianzhou, I must report it to the general...}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
